channel.title: 317 staff panel code?
channel.description: Is there a code to turn your music tab into a staff panel? It would have things like mute, kick, ban, and ipban. All you would have to do is click the button then enter the person's name. I have seen this before on a server, but I would very much like the code. If anyone has this code, can I please use it? I promise to give you complete credit for it.
